{"tid":105984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本圖書館推出「女性專用席」防痴漢","createTime":"2017-02-03T09:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T12:16:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21981087c8e100a3e7863c7d8e4e28511a0adaaf","tid":105984,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>日本圖書館推「女性專用席」防痴漢 壽命只1天</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-02  16:49<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕公共場所因為閒雜人多，有時會有色狼藉機伸魔爪。最近日本1間圖書館就推出女性專用席，防止女性遭到色狼性騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，日本北海道大學附屬圖書館在<strong>去年接獲6件性騷擾通報，之後館方雖貼上海報、加強巡邏，仍無法制止色狼伸狼爪。</strong>圖書館在今年1月底又接獲通報，有女學生遭色狼騷擾，館方於是將圖書館其中1區劃成「女性專用席」，禁止男生入坐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/2/images/bigPic/400_400/phpTXjejq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F2%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpTXjejq.jpg&h=23bc8880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本1間圖書館推出女性專用席，防止女性遭到色狼性騷擾。（圖擷自twitter）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/2/images/bigPic/400_400/php6vE2GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F2%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2Fphp6vE2GJ.jpg&h=59a6238c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖書館製做的告示顯示，成立女性專用席，是要保護打瞌睡的女生，不被痴漢性騷擾。（圖擷自twitter）<br />\n    <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/2/images/bigPic/400_400/phpaLI5Dq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F2%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpaLI5Dq.jpg&h=daad3690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為男性反彈太大，女性專用席只持續1天就喊停。（圖擷自twitter）<br />\n<br />\n雖然圖書館這樣做是為了保護女性，卻引來許多男性不滿，有網友就指出，圖書館有1/3的範圍都被劃成女性專用席。此外，圖書館指出，會成立女性專用席是要保護打瞌睡的女生，不會被痴漢性騷擾，許多網友也對此有意見，他們認為圖書館並非是睡覺的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n在許多網友的批判下，北海道大學附屬圖書館的女性專用席只維持了1天，館方決定另尋方法，阻止色狼在館內做出性騷擾行為。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1963087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1963087&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c767e3f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1963087&h=973a5f5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1963087</a>"},{"pid":"e551b51a1d01674d155062fe90d84e4db1af455c","tid":105984,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"香港都應該整番個防廢老專用席"},{"pid":"dd18bdf6533c3e4bd30cbc3462488b0cebeeeb7b","tid":105984,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24d546cac6c31e28965de497f4cc4e1b57125b94","tid":105984,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"香港幾時出個女性專月ATM"},{"pid":"d80fca50d186ffb01ba25150d2318ea8fed80ba7","tid":105984,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"直頭劃區男女以後分開生活咪得，攪咁撚多嘢"},{"pid":"9dcdf259e78338b329eaff01d5102331331e8e3f","tid":105984,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直頭劃區男女以後分開生活咪得，攪咁撚多嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔得，如果身邊冇晒啲低賤男人，點顯得女人嘅高貴"},{"pid":"d8f6d8bbe98a283923001e41cce5358f072d820e","tid":105984,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379b47b0d4946b213fe5b449edbbe369cd395ea4","tid":105984,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"不能作聲"},{"pid":"89a212379933e0326652f17387f551de6fc114e4","tid":105984,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直頭劃區男女以後分開生活咪得，攪咁撚多嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔得，如果身邊冇晒啲低賤男人，點顯得女人嘅高貴</blockquote><br />\nmacross 巨人族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51e6c8dae1b861f84be659cdf9f9b050fdec164","tid":105984,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"女權撚死左去邊 仲唔出黎講兩嘴嘅？"},{"pid":"69c2c8d46f7915701741e26e54fee9c41eb9f36f","tid":105984,"uid":72968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"成個月前既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4693a8003fe6e396cdbb2e594cbedcc01065208d","tid":105984,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個月前既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又唔貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就真係孤陋寡聞<br />\n未睇過嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}